{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8566494}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n No. 714, de 31 de Julio de 1992 de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n, rectif&#xED;case la Resoluci&#xF3;n No. 257, de 1992, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, por la cual se autoriz&#xF3; a PESQUERA LOA SUR S.A., R.U.T. No. 95.059.000-9, domiciliada en Santiago, para ampliar las actividades pesqueras extractivas, en su numeral 2&#xB0; en el sentido de indicar que las caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas de las naves en &#xE9;l individualizadas son las siguientes:</div><div class=\"p\">Nombre&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;Loa 12&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;Loa 14&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2595&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  2598</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  40,22 m.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  40,22 m.</div><div class=\"p\">Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8,60 m.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8,60 m.</div><div class=\"p\">Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  6,8 m.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  6,8 m.</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.G.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  464,7 t.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  464,0 t.</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.N.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  233,5 t.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  233,5 t.</div><div class=\"p\">Capacidad de bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 500,0 m3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  500,0 m3.</div><div class=\"p\">Arte de pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco</div><br></div>", "i": 8566495}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 31 de